{"tid":1528327,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"做法可能唔完美，但絕對有改善空間","createTime":"2019-09-01T13:38:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T09:42:41.000Z","uid":286135,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4eee9ba524318cdfc205a650d2ad882f73453f11","tid":1528327,"uid":286135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T13:38:17.000Z","msg":"今日既爆閘行動引起極多淺黃淺藍質疑，包括我家中既淺黃<br />\n第一個回應係:佢地既做法可能唔完美，有改善既空間<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">進一步解釋</span></strong></strong></span>：琴日地鐵配合警察係太子旺角發動恐怖襲擊<br />\n示威者希望對港鐵施加壓力，促使港鐵回應。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果有人質疑係示威者郁手先就澄清呢個唔係事實：</span></span><br />\n有市民於車廂裡與中年男子發生口角，並有熱心市民懷疑該名男子持有武器企圖襲擊市民<br />\n於是群眾於生死存亡之際決定行使公民拘捕權，將該名男子暫時拘捕，<br />\n豈不知遭到該名男子猛烈反抗，隨後男子的增援（香港警察）到場支援，<br />\n令大量無辜市民受傷，關於口角一事，做法可能唔完美，但絕對有改善空間<br />\n<br />\n呢個完全唔係辯駁，辯解，只係對事件既陳述<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />正評：個po有用，繼續開po指點迷津<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />負評：一早識講啦，洗撚你教，留翻quota開其他po啦"},{"pid":"a9522909343cb1dc0d92e592717871cd0e7a9ba2","tid":1528327,"uid":286135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T13:38:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5c89e336920336dc04ccd4ff0fbc585fad107cfb","tid":1528327,"uid":286135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T13:38:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"947d82340ad9c4f79d4791fe86276936eaec3b01","tid":1528327,"uid":286135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T13:38:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6f61864eac3bf6edda769b2d8c1f6397a9707e65","tid":1528327,"uid":127202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T13:39:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V4epjHE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV4epjHE.jpg&h=c196038e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ad280043603b6d2e94a8895221e00e